to add CORS in your node API install:
npm install --save cors

to push code on heroku git;
git push heroku master


in google chrom new version CORS is not enabled:
Add a plugin :Allow CORS: Access-Control-Allow-Origin



steps do deploy API on Heroku:
1)create a file in project with name procfile
2)navigate to folder in cmd and type:Login Heroku
3)create name - heroku create apidemonodejs
git add .
git commit -m "a"
git push heroku master